data.description: Waterfront living at its finest! This remarkable 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is nestled on a navigable canal in the highly sought-after Cedar Island community. Boasting a modern and bright interior, this home is a true gem. The recent updates throughout add to the home's appeal, while the standout feature—a home cargo lift/elevator—makes daily tasks a breeze.  The interior of this home is a perfect blend of modern design and functionality. The open floor plan allows for a seamless flow between the living spaces, creating an providing that beautiful evening glow during sunsets.   The kitchen consists of sleek cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, and ample counter space. Whether you're hosting a dinner party or enjoying a casual meal with loved ones, this kitchen provides everything you need.  One of the unique features of this home is the mezzanine deck below. This versatile space is perfect for entertaining guests, with plenty of room for playing pool, grilling or an outdoor bar area.   The navigable canal allows for easy access to the water, making it convenient to explore some of the best fishing and boating in the Gulf of Mexico.
